Here is the task in a structured plan:

1. find a phrase formatted like this: `XX.YY ($USD)` in the EMAIL text,
2. if multiple such phrases are found, return all the found phrases separated by `|`, and format them one per line

I have implemented that, here's the code:

scss

const EMAIL = `

On Wed, Mar 9, 2022, 9:35 AM Booba Too <too@booba.net> wrote:
  
  Hey there, Lord Moss, how is your broccoli garden growing? You have any ideas how to reduce the amount of aphids that keep eating my succulents? 

Yes, I saw yesterdays episode of American Dad. Your "I'm a little Teapot" dance was epic. Sad though that Roger still got kicked out of Teterboro Airport. Of the 9 dancing companies, The Rockettes is the only one in New York, the others are in Florida, so I'm not sure how we can work that into a field trip. The owner of the school is yet to be identified. In the show itself Steve suggests it might be Bill Gates or even Stan Marsh. The way he looks up when he say's "Stan Marsh" sure makes it seem like he's considering himself. The Wikipedia page mentions that in a commentary the creators say the correct answer is Steven Bochco. I'm not going to bother figuring that one out. A handgun can weigh up to 3 pounds.  

Can I stop by with some crenchy broccoli on Sunday at 2:30 for roast beef sandwiches? 

Wait are you actually competent with firearms? Can we meet at the range then? I can bring my brother's .45 to show you what makes Americas's great.
  
  
  In the meantime I'll see if the pest control store has anything for aphids, I have another 30 minutes to kill before it opens.

  Frowningly yours,  
  Booba Too
  p.s. Saw this while fact-checking my letter https://encyclopediadramatica.es/John_Wolfe_apostrophe
  
  <stuff about money I don't care about>
  
  By the way, I made the words in the PS look like the link, but it's not actually it, I'm still not dumb enough to publicly post that, this is just a replacement image from https://lamebook.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/modals.jpg with the caption removed. Still made my eyes burn.
  
  
  <!-- Apple Mail APS -->
  <meta name="apple-margin" content="0.015in">
  <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
`

const foundMatches = EMAIL.match(/\$\s?(\d+).(\d+)/)?.slice(1)?.map((eli) => (+eli[1] + +eli[2])) || [];
const results = {
  value: foundMatches[0] || "unknown",
  matched: foundMatches.length > 0,
};

Please let me know if you have questions or any corrections to the task.
